How to run:

* make sure you have python >= 2.7.9 installed, pip updated (https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installing/#upgrading-pip)
  and virtualenv installed (pip install virtualenv)
* unzip the file in some dir and cd to scrum dir
* create a virtual env in the dir (eg virtualenv newenv)
* activate the virtual env (eg. 'source newenv/bin/activate')
* install the dependencies (pip install -r requirements.txt)
* run the scrum.py file in src subdir: 'python src/scrum.py -h' or 'python src/scrum.py'
* To execute the tests, just execute: 'nosetests --with-doctest'